quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  90,1,"Nay! I swear by this city"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  90,2,"– this city wherein you have been rendered violable–"{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,3,"and I swear by the parent and his offspring:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,4,"Verily We have created man into toil and hardship."{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,5,"Does he think that no one can overpower him?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,6,"He says: “I have squandered enormous wealth.”"{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,7,"Does he believe that none has seen him?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,8,"Did We not grant him two eyes,"
  90,9,"and a tongue and two lips?"{1},footnotes:1:1
  90,10,"And did We not show him the two highroads (of good and evil)?"{1},footnotes:1:1